        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎬 Cinematic Color Grade\n\nGive any photo a graded, filmic look — no AI, all deterministic GPU color ops.\n\n**Pipeline:** Image → exposure & contrast → split toning (teal shadows / orange highlights) → vignette → output.\n\n**Try this:** push `contrast` and `shadow_saturation` for a stronger look, or swap the split-tone hues (e.g. shadow 240 / highlight 30) for a different mood."
        },
